{"id":"24005","name":"記憶永不落幕","rarity":5,"path":"Memory","desc":"不論繁華的、荒涼的、短暫的、漫長的……每一顆星球，每一個瞬間皆在發生無數的事件。\n那凝結的歷史一觸便融化於手中，化作淚水自世界的眼眸流淌而下——\n有人說，那是多麼沉重的淚水，凝聚的歲月足以令永恆褪色。\n有人說，那是多麼美妙的故事，悲哀澄澈，歡悅明靜，其間不夾雜一絲虛偽。\n銀河靜默流淌，祂不語，只是凝望——\n凝望著，等待著它們成為「記憶」。","icon":"icon/light_cone/24005.png","preview":"image/light_cone_preview/24005.png","portrait":"image/light_cone_portrait/24005.png","ranks":{"id":"24005","skill":"收取","desc":"使裝備者的速度提高#1[f1]%。裝備者施放戰技後，使我方全體造成的傷害提高#2[i]%，持續#3[i]回合。","params":[[0.06,0.08,3],[0.075,0.1,3],[0.09,0.12,3],[0.105,0.14,3],[0.12,0.16,3]],"properties":[[{"type":"SpeedAddedRatio","value":0.06}],[{"type":"SpeedAddedRatio","value":0.075}],[{"type":"SpeedAddedRatio","value":0.09}],[{"type":"SpeedAddedRatio","value":0.105}],[{"type":"SpeedAddedRatio","value":0.12}]]},"promotions":{"id":"24005","values":[{"hp":{"base":48,"step":7.2},"atk":{"base":24,"step":3.6},"def":{"base":18,"step":2.7}},{"hp":{"base":105.6,"step":7.2},"atk":{"base":52.8,"step":3.6},"def":{"base":39.6,"step":2.7}},{"hp":{"base":182.4,"step":7.2},"atk":{"base":91.2,"step":3.6},"def":{"base":68.4,"step":2.7}},{"hp":{"base":259.2,"step":7.2},"atk":{"base":129.6,"step":3.6},"def":{"base":97.2,"step":2.7}},{"hp":{"base":336,"step":7.2},"atk":{"base":168,"step":3.6},"def":{"base":126,"step":2.7}},{"hp":{"base":412.8,"step":7.2},"atk":{"base":206.4,"step":3.6},"def":{"base":154.8,"step":2.7}},{"hp":{"base":489.6,"step":7.2},"atk":{"base":244.8,"step":3.6},"def":{"base":183.6,"step":2.7}}],"materials":[[{"id":"2","num":5000},{"id":"111001","num":8}],[{"id":"2","num":10000},{"id":"110251","num":4},{"id":"111001","num":12}],[{"id":"2","num":20000},{"id":"110252","num":4},{"id":"111002","num":8}],[{"id":"2","num":50000},{"id":"110252","num":8},{"id":"111002","num":12}],[{"id":"2","num":100000},{"id":"110253","num":5},{"id":"111003","num":6}],[{"id":"2","num":200000},{"id":"110253","num":10},{"id":"111003","num":8}],[]]}}